_sText: This is a newer version of my gg_sl_cross2 map. The skybox has been changed (it still needs a 3d skybox), slightly altered lighting (brightness), and added section to the right of each spawn to give players more variety. It also has 32 spawn points. Many of the textures have been fixed. This is probably my favorite map of all my creations. It can also be played as a gungame map or as an AIM map (has buyzones).
